Orth
Copyright (c) 2025-present, zombie12138 and contributors.

Orth is a fork of XXL-JOB (https://github.com/xuxueli/xxl-job).

Original work:
Copyright (c) 2015-present, xuxueli.
Licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0.

Modifications from upstream XXL-JOB (per GPLv3 Section 5(a)):
- Renamed project from XXL-JOB to Orth; changed groupId to com.abyss
- Replaced JSP admin UI with React 19 + TypeScript + Ant Design 5 SPA (orth-ui/)
- Added JWT authentication with role-based access control
- Added SuperTask pattern (batch copy from template jobs)
- Added batch trigger with logical schedule time support
- Added job import/export (JSON)
- Added concurrent execution block strategy
- Migrated to Spring Boot 3.5, Java 17, Jakarta EE namespace
- Redesigned REST API with OpenAPI conventions
- Added architecture documentation (arch/)
- Converted codebase and documentation to English

